data.description: Looking for an affordable three bedroom home this is it. New septic system in 2021 with many updates throughout the home. First floor has kitchen, dinning room, living room, small den & one full bathroom.  Upstairs you will find three bedrooms.  This home currently is heated and cooled with two mini splits that do the job just fine however gas is available in this area. Seller has never occupied this property it was used strictly as a rental, buyer and buyers agent to verify all information and perform their due diligence. Selling strictly as is buyer to be responsible for all inspections and certifications needed to close.     Seller is the spouse of the Listing REALTOR.  Property will be active once tenants vacate
